  readFiles[4]: workflow-harness/mcp-server/src/gates/dod-l3.ts,workflow-harness/mcp-server/src/gates/dod-l4-delta.ts,workflow-harness/mcp-server/src/phases/registry.ts,workflow-harness/mcp-server/src/gates/dod-l4-requirements.ts
  warnings[3]: analyzeArtifact関数の全面再実装がimpact_analysisで詳細コスト見積もりが必要,dod-l4-requirements.tsのハードコードパス問題はrequirementsフェーズTOON移行で別途対処,minLines・sectionDensityの閾値はTOON形式用に再定義が必要
